---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = "高雄失智症居家照護｜專業失智照顧服務";
const description = "宇涵提供專業失智症居家照護服務，運用實證照護技巧，穩定長者情緒、延緩退化，為失智長者打造安全舒適的居家生活環境。";
const canonicalURL = new URL("/services/dementia-care/", Astro.site);
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalURL={canonicalURL}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" slot="head">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Service",
      "name": "高雄失智症居家照護",
      "description": "專業失智症照護，運用實證照護技巧，穩定長者情緒、延緩退化，提供安全的生活環境",
      "provider": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "宇涵居家照護"},
      "areaServed": {"@type": "City", "name": "高雄市"},
      "serviceType": "失智症照護",
      "url": "https://yuhanhomecare.com/services/dementia-care/"
    }
  </script>

  <section class="relative bg-[#fcfaf6] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-[#efe5d5] opacity-30 rounded-bl-[100px]"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24 relative">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb" class="mb-4">
          <ol class="flex text-sm text-[#6d5d50]">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors">首頁</a></li>
            <li class="mx-2">/</li>
            <li><a href="/services/" class="hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors">服務項目</a></li>
            <li class="mx-2">/</li>
            <li class="text-[#2b221c] font-medium" aria-current="page">失智照護</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-4 leading-tight">高雄失智症居家照護</h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">專業失智照護，用愛與耐心守護每一個記憶</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <img src="/images/blog-dementia.jpg" alt="高雄失智症居家照護" class="w-full h-80 object-cover rounded-2xl mb-10 shadow-md" loading="lazy" width="800" height="320" />

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">認識失智症</h2>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">失智症是一種進行性退化的腦部疾病，主要影響患者的記憶力、思考能力、判斷力與日常生活功能。常見的失智症類型包括阿茲海默症（佔所有病例的60-70%）、血管性失智症、路易氏體失智症、額顳葉型失智症等。隨著病情發展，患者會逐漸喪失獨立生活的能力，需要越來越多的照護支持。</p>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">根據台灣失智症協會的統計，台灣目前失智症人口已超過30萬人，隨著高齡化社會的加速，預計到2030年失智症人口將突破50萬人。在高雄市，失智症長者的照護需求也日益增加。許多家庭面臨失智症照護的挑戰，家屬往往因為不了解病情、缺乏照護技巧而感到無助與挫折。</p>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">失智症的病程通常分為輕度、中度與重度三個階段。輕度失智症患者可能出現記憶力減退、忘記近期發生的事、重複提問等症狀，但基本生活功能尚可維持。中度失智症患者則需要更多的生活協助，可能出現迷路、日夜顛倒、情緒不穩、懷疑他人等症狀。重度失智症患者則幾乎完全喪失生活自理能力，需要全方位的照顧。</p>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-10">宇涵居家照護深入了解失智症的特性與照護挑戰，我們的失智照護服務旨在幫助失智長者維持現有能力、延緩病情退化、提升生活品質，同時減輕家屬的照護負擔與壓力。我們的看護人員接受過失智照護專業訓練，熟悉失智症的症狀表現與照護技巧，能夠以專業、耐心與愛心照顧失智長者。</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">失智照護服務內容</h2>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">宇涵的失智照護服務涵蓋失智長者生活的各個面向，我們採取以人為本的照護理念，尊重每位長者的個性、喜好與過去的生活經驗，設計個人化的照護方案：</p>
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">情緒安撫與行為管理</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">失智長者常出現焦慮、躁動、重複行為、遊走等行為症狀。我們的看護人員學習過非藥物介入技巧，透過轉移注意力、撫慰情緒、維持規律作息等方式，幫助長者穩定情緒，減少行為問題的發生。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">認知促進活動</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">安排適合的認知訓練活動，如懷舊療法、音樂治療、圖卡認知、簡單手作等，刺激長者的大腦活動，延緩認知退化速度，同時增加生活的樂趣與成就感。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">規律作息安排</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">建立穩定的生活作息，包括固定的用餐時間、活動時間、休息時間與就寢時間。規律的生活有助於減少失智長者的焦慮與混亂感，讓他們更有安全感。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">安全防護與照顧</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">預防走失、跌倒、燙傷等安全風險，必要時陪同外出。留意長者身體狀況變化，協助用藥、進食、沐浴等日常活動，確保基本生活需求。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">生活起居協助</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">協助失智長者完成日常活動，如穿衣、盥洗、進食、如廁等，同時給予長者盡可能自己完成的机会，維持殘存功能與尊嚴。</p></div>
            <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] p-6 rounded-xl"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3"><div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#8b621f] bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#8b621f]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"></path></svg></div><h3 class="font-bold text-[#2b221c]">家屬溝通與支持</h3></div><p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed">定時向家屬回報長者的狀況，分享照護經驗與技巧，提供情緒支持，幫助家屬更了解失智症，學習與患者正確的溝通方式與照護方法。</p></div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">失智照護專業技巧</h2>
          <p class="text-[#6d5d50] leading-relaxed mb-6">宇涵的看護人員接受專業失智照護訓練，具備以下專業照護能力：</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#8b621f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">1</span></div><div><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">驗證療法：</strong><span class="text-[#6d5d50]">不與失智長者爭論或糾正其錯誤認知，而是進入他們的世界，認同他們的感受，減少衝突與挫折感。</span></div></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#8b621f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">2</span></div><div><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">現實導向訓練：</strong><span class="text-[#6d5d50]">透過日期、時間、地點的提醒，幫助輕度失智長者維持對現實的認知，減少混亂感。</span></div></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#8b621f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">3</span></div><div><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">懷舊療法：</strong><span class="text-[#6d5d50]">透過老照片、音樂、舊物等媒介，引導長者回憶過去的美好時光，增進情感連結與自我價值感。</span></div></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#8b621f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">4</span></div><div><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">音樂治療：</strong><span class="text-[#6d5d50]">播放長者熟悉的歌曲或音樂，有助於穩定情緒、喚醒記憶，並創造愉悅的氛圍。</span></div></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#8b621f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">5</span></div><div><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">感官刺激活動：</strong><span class="text-[#6d5d50]">透過觸覺、嗅覺、味覺、視覺、聽覺等感官活動，維持大腦的神經連結，刺激認知功能。</span></div></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#8b621f] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1"><span class="text-white text-xs font-bold">6</span></div><div><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">簡化指令溝通：</strong><span class="text-[#6d5d50]">使用簡單、清楚的語句與長者溝通，一次只給一個指令，搭配手勢與表情，提高理解度。</span></div></li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">費用參考</h2>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
            <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
              <thead><tr class="bg-[#2b221c] text-[#fcfaf6]"><th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">服務方案</th><th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">時段</th><th class="px-6 py-4 font-semibold">參考費用</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-[#efe5d5]">
                <tr class="hover:bg-[#fcfaf6]"><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#2b221c]">日間照護</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#6d5d50]">12小時</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#8b621f] font-semibold">$2,400 - $2,800 /日</td></tr>
                <tr class="hover:bg-[#fcfaf6]"><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#2b221c]">全天候照護</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#6d5d50]">24小時</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#8b621f] font-semibold">$2,800 - $3,200 /日</td></tr>
                <tr class="hover:bg-[#fcfaf6]"><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#2b221c]">日間陪伴</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#6d5d50]">8小時</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-[#8b621f] font-semibold">$2,000 - $2,400 /日</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#6d5d50] mb-10">* 失智照護因需要更專業的技巧與耐心，費用略高於一般居家看護。實際費用依失智程度與服務內容評估。</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-6">為什麼選擇宇涵的失智照護？</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-10">
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start"><div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#8b621f] text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">✓</div><div><p class="text-[#6d5d50]"><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">專業失智照護訓練：</strong>所有失智照護看護皆完成失智症專業訓練課程，熟悉失智症的症狀、行為問題與照護技巧。</p></div></div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start"><div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#8b621f] text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">✓</div><div><p class="text-[#6d5d50]"><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">耐心與愛心：</strong>失智長者需要更多的理解與包容，我們精挑細選具備耐心、愛心與同理心的照護人員。</p></div></div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start"><div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#8b621f] text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">✓</div><div><p class="text-[#6d5d50]"><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">個人化照護計畫：</strong>針對每位失智長者的病程、個性、喜好、生活背景，制定專屬的照護計畫。</p></div></div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 items-start"><div class="w-8 h-8 bg-[#8b621f] text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold text-sm">✓</div><div><p class="text-[#6d5d50]"><strong class="text-[#2b221c]">家屬教育與支持：</strong>我們不只是照顧長者，也提供家屬照護知識與情緒支持，幫助整個家庭更好地面對失智症的挑戰。</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="bg-[#fcfaf6] rounded-2xl p-6 sticky top-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-4">其他服務項目</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
              <li><a href="/services/home-care/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 居家看護</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/hospital-care/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 醫院看護</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/elderly-care/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 長者陪伴</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/post-surgery/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 術後照顧</a></li>
              <li><a href="/services/temporary-care/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#6d5d50] hover:text-[#8b621f] transition-colors"><span class="text-[#8b621f]">→</span> 臨時看護</a></li>
            </ul>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#2b221c] mb-4">快速聯絡</h3>
            <a href="tel:0935803258" class="block w-full text-center bg-[#8b621f] text-white py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-[#6d4a18] transition-colors mb-3"><span class="text-sm block opacity-80">24小時服務專線</span><span class="text-lg">0935-803-258</span></a>
            <a href="/contact/" class="block w-full text-center border-2 border-[#8b621f] text-[#8b621f] py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-[#8b621f] hover:text-white transition-colors">線上諮詢表單</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-[#2b221c]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#fcfaf6] mb-4">為失智長者打造安心的生活</h2>
      <p class="text-[#efe5d5] mb-8 leading-relaxed">宇涵失智照護團隊隨時為您提供專業諮詢與服務，讓我們一起守護最愛的家人。</p>
